extendedInfo.description: Use Nyheterna to follow news (nyheter) from Sweden and the rest of Scandinavia in Scandinavian languages.Read local news from the closest news sources.Read subject-specific news from all sources specializing in that subject.Listen to the latest news podcast from the local area.Listen to a radio show covering a specific subject, which you found by reading the newsfeed (RSS) from the radio show.477 Swedish-speaking news sources from Sweden.115 Danish-speaking news sources from Denmark.45 Norwegian-speaking news sources from Norway.18 Swedish-speaking news sources from Finland.Select which country or countries you would like to see news and news sources from.Enjoy news by listening to podcasts, by reading RSS feeds, by reading mobile websites or by reading regular websites.Save favorite news sources and group them. Read RSS news from all favorite news sources in a group.Specify the page the app should start from. For instance: Start from the page showing RSS news from my second group of favorite news sources.
